The gas? Oh the gas cooker - well it was one - one of these wee cookers that you tipped up at that time. It was on the hob, on what you called the hob at - of the range, you just tipped it - down at the time when you
 were being to make anything and tipped it up at the rod you see. That was how it worked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9641210 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12392121\charrsid10055426 
