itchen table you know - you - spread - you - you don't see many about nowadays but they're all done away with. Aye, you know, with - two leafs on them you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9641210 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12392121\charrsid10055426 What happened for your midday meal, would you be home for your midday meal?

