Well I did that - I did that job 'til I got a - I got offered another job in the provision line of - making up oddments you know, at Coopers at that time. That was the time Coopers were in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Sauchiehall Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9641210 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12392121\charrsid10055426 So how long did you do the first job for?
