oh aye. Och aye, I used to travel all over the place, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9641210 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12392121\charrsid10055426 Did either of you or your wife go to any clubs or institutes or pubs?
